data.description: VA ASSUMABLE LOAN.  2.625% INTERTEST RATE With acceptable offer. Step into this lovely home. You'll be captivated by the interior archways & intricate decorative tile work, infusing each room with character & charm. These spacious bedrooms are a rare gem. The open floor plan effortlessly connects the living, dining, & kitchen spaces, creating a welcoming environment for daily living. The kitchen is a true showpiece, adorned with marble & granite countertops, an exquisite backsplash, & top-of-the-line stainless steel appliances. Ample storage. Every room is bathed in the soft glow of recessed lighting. Fabulous built-ins to showcase treasured collectibles. Screened patio with a wet bar perfect for game nights & entertaining. This home is equipped with a TWH, ensuring you have a continuous supply of hot water. Make this beautiful home yours!
